{"tid":1023542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【假新聞】【factcheck】「烤肉式用刑 中國凌虐新疆人手法曝光」實為誤會","createTime":"2019-02-16T00:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T12:22:20.000Z","uid":138409,"like":67,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"bd41db133a6c6b47051756b6f80431fd4151de80","tid":1023542,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T00:19:52.000Z","msg":"峰迴路轉真係估你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡直比得上林子健單嘢<br />\n<br />\n睇之前戴返頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢篇fact check並<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔係</span></span>要否認新疆有集中營拘禁穆斯林 / 否認中共對新疆穆斯林嘅逼害<br />\n純粹係針對呢幅圖所引發嘅新聞進行查核<br />\n<br />\n今次炒車亦都唔算連登嘅責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至少響轉載篇假新聞當日<br />\n應該未有現成嘅factcheck<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<a href=\"https://tfc-taiwan.org.tw/articles/379?fbclid=IwAR3w5FJL7ldem0-v3fcuciwIVPnL-ZrhwkIgnzU057lwYLgre33Gq68nWq4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftfc-taiwan.org.tw%2Farticles%2F379%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3w5FJL7ldem0-v3fcuciwIVPnL-ZrhwkIgnzU057lwYLgre33Gq68nWq4&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qjC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=60db2581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tfc-taiwan.org.tw/articles/379?fbclid=IwAR3w5FJL7ldem0-v3fcuciwIVPnL-ZrhwkIgnzU057lwYLgre33Gq68nWq4</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">多家媒體近日引用網路影片據以報導，標題如：「烤肉式用刑 中國凌虐新疆人手法曝光」。經查：<br />\n<br />\n查核中心透過管道與影片中當事者本人取得聯繫，證實此影片是角色扮演活動的影片，並非警察刑求民眾的錄影。影片拍攝地點是佈置成監獄風格的私人場地，並非真正的監獄。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因此，「中國當局使用『烤肉式行刑』凌虐新疆人」等報導是誤用民眾角色扮演影片的錯誤新聞。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n背景<br />\n<br />\n多家媒體近日引用網路影片據以報導，標題如「烤肉式用刑 中國凌虐新疆人手法曝光」等等，內容稱：「從新疆逃脫至土耳其的東突厥斯坦民眾，在臉書上PO出1段中國警方虐待新疆人士的影片，從中能見新疆人士穿著藍色囚衣被五花大綁在刑具上，由1名員警負責拷問，另有員警操控刑具，他們對新疆民眾表示『你違規啊，現在受罰啦，開動！』示意開始用刑。」（見下圖一）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xtkfLSX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxtkfLSX.png&h=2363e134&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mQkWvj9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmQkWvj9.png&h=67c51b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a8Lzg0e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa8Lzg0e.png&h=c86e6dd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖一、媒體引用網路影片指出中國政府使用「烤肉式行刑」來凌虐新疆人<br />\n<br />\n查核<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">爭議點：報導中影片內容是否為「中國警方虐待新疆人士」的影片？</span><br />\n<br />\n某位民眾在社群媒體分享新聞報導時，另一位民眾小金（化名）回應指出自己就是該影片中當事者，並說明影片內容為他本人正在進行角色扮演。（見下圖二）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eNL0cyM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeNL0cyM.jpg&h=d3e0642b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖二、民眾留言說明自己就是影片中當事者本人，正在進行角色扮演。<br />\n<br />\n查核中心透過管道與小金取得聯絡，小金提出原始影片與現場拍攝之其他照片等證據供查核中心檢視。照片中之衣物顏色、款式等與新聞報導所引用影片中之衣物顏色、款式相同；在旁擔任警察角色之參與者衣物裝扮也與影片中相同；小金提供之原始影片也與新聞報導引用之影片相同；小金提供之照片、影片中之背景、物品、佈置等等，也與新聞影片相同。（見下圖三）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5GCeNc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5GCeNc.png&h=61d5b80f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eVdw3FB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeVdw3FB.png&h=308b230f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EWDpEd6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEWDpEd6.png&h=6e398cb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖三、民眾提供當次角色扮演之其他照片（經當事者同意發布）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FUnU1sw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFUnU1sw.png&h=a5fdc40c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖四、民眾提供原始影片至查核中心（此截圖經當事者同意發布）<br />\n<br />\n小金說明，此影片是自己上傳放在社交媒體上，並且說明身上穿的衣服雖然是真正中國監獄的監獄服，但是地點不是在監獄，而是佈置成監獄風格的私人場所，擔任警察角色的也不是真正的獄警。（如下圖五）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTNJUNM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTNJUNM.jpg&h=aeb9d32e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖五、民眾指出影片地點不是中國監獄，而是布置跟監獄相同的私人場地。（此對話經當事者同意發布）<br />\n<br />\n綜上所述，「中國當局使用『烤肉式行刑』凌虐新疆人」等報導是誤用民眾角色扮演影片的錯誤新聞。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">結論<br />\n<br />\n當事者本人出面證實，此影片是角色扮演活動的影片，並非警察刑求民眾的錄影。影片拍攝地點是佈置成監獄風格的私人場地，並非真正的監獄。</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea1e58b39cf30460a5a90898680aac01ab95bb79","tid":1023542,"uid":138409,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T00:22:09.000Z","msg":"有關中國打壓（包括新疆人）宗教自由嘅新聞<br />\n詳見<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/videos/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fvideos%2F&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qjC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=3bb93c69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.bitterwinter.org/videos/</a>"},{"pid":"cd470d8fdd2834c1792a04921f056b01220d19e9","tid":1023542,"uid":35815,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T00:25:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a177592e44c3e661500bc334c17721fb3703d4f0","tid":1023542,"uid":33907,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T00:27:41.000Z","msg":"都話 用烤用式緊係烤豬肉先有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咁逼佢地食"},{"pid":"896958b4b9360b07d49fd4abbb72903873211f6c","tid":1023542,"uid":38523,"like":63,"dislike":7,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T00:27:44.000Z","msg":"呢招成日見啦<br />\n專登放假新聞出來<br />\n等第日真野流出都冇人信"},{"pid":"2be4a50eaf1962132b82b4d365ca7229c03ad7e7","tid":1023542,"uid":138409,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"896958b4b9360b07d49fd4abbb72903873211f6c","tid":1023542,"uid":38523,"like":63,"dislike":7,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T00:27:44.000Z","msg":"呢招成日見啦<br />\n專登放假新聞出來<br />\n等第日真野流出都冇人信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T00:31:30.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n所以真係要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過講真呢個case又真係好難怪啲人輕信<br />\n中國呢啲國家乜都做得出又劣跡斑斑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你點估到真相咁離奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3a4848dc8e68b5fa6aa7be6b582e0ffbbfc3c6","tid":1023542,"uid":38472,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T00:36:45.000Z","msg":"好似一早有人都話炒車味濃。 等睇共媒又拎嚟打飛機又話假新聞多。"},{"pid":"0f97d863d4e6d431e4c385d5dccb9cfacfb12fb8","tid":1023542,"uid":64191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T00:37:26.000Z","msg":"呢單野初初有質疑過，但估唔到引到當事人澄清"},{"pid":"ad7815d62f5ecf0126edef67ae9f6de8a7fb20d3","tid":1023542,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T00:38:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ac403c744e4c78834c17ddfe2b70bcb2511c707d","tid":1023542,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:06:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"32bf8b596444f1462e5b7fd21b34dcf2648b39a2","tid":1023542,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:08:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"341fa204fe070aadc2ae3971250e60b88e90939a","tid":1023542,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:10:17.000Z","msg":"唔會有人理你的"},{"pid":"4734ea40537300cba5986dbf50a5eeb87f1bc152","tid":1023542,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:15:17.000Z","msg":"注定失敗"},{"pid":"0d86b46d92d9c392d8d8bcfdbc3f4c2e803c5234","tid":1023542,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:17:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"72daada75896be0301492c74d99b65680ec52e2b","tid":1023542,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:21:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dfc4cb1fea48563e46647f86e262539725c7f4c4","tid":1023542,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:28:40.000Z","msg":"一個鐘只能自推一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14119232e9e1abc98af5ac995caac8b81e41eef","tid":1023542,"uid":20816,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:31:05.000Z","msg":"做啲有意義的事啦<br />\n擺明用fake news挑起仇恨又點?"},{"pid":"892772f714285a47116bf5eb8e59c8189de36ee0","tid":1023542,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:31:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa40dd0c71460f2dc522dc0a0781c6847f521fb7","tid":1023542,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:37:46.000Z","msg":"只要達到令大家憎中共即可<br />\n理得佢係咪fake news<br />\n咁關心回教恐怖份子唔見關注下關塔那摩灣監獄?<br />\n好似輪姦班回教恐怖份子添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d62e04bf6439531e163bee873bc1e9080a630da","tid":1023542,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:39:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"27dec071ffaa5be765e0ef326f3f93e22869ea11","tid":1023542,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:40:50.000Z","msg":"但係點 check 呢個所謂嘅 face check 係咪 fact?"},{"pid":"814450acf75db90d87a880f3e136a7e6dc3d2afc","tid":1023542,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:40:51.000Z","msg":"駁唔到喺度喪推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f8389afd512c5408e46542213ad4f472439270","tid":1023542,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27dec071ffaa5be765e0ef326f3f93e22869ea11","tid":1023542,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:40:50.000Z","msg":"但係點 check 呢個所謂嘅 face check 係咪 fact?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:42:08.000Z","msg":"可能用支槍指住條友㗎"},{"pid":"47447b1ecb5a563360eb42b32b478de12a1e9c6b","tid":1023542,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:45:18.000Z","msg":"Op呢啲左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2103d49ccd668158177c57a984045174b4df1d","tid":1023542,"uid":138409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"27dec071ffaa5be765e0ef326f3f93e22869ea11","tid":1023542,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:40:50.000Z","msg":"但係點 check 呢個所謂嘅 face check 係咪 fact?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:46:48.000Z","msg":"我只能夠話<br />\n按照現有佢畀嘅證據來睇<br />\n（相片、影片上傳紀錄之類）<br />\n有理由相信fact check嘅可信性&gt;最初新聞報導<br />\n<br />\n當然如果有新證據出現懷疑fact check造假<br />\n咁就係另一回事<br />\n問題係你要懷疑，都要提出證據"},{"pid":"37e936704c8fc1193fbea38e83c5a64482105511","tid":1023542,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:47:33.000Z","msg":"選擇性回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d139f5e29d7ac6471d2642230025eef21ecf49c","tid":1023542,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:48:53.000Z","msg":"估都估到<br />\n真既話中共會比人拍片咩？"},{"pid":"d55dfb564f4fadd6d69b1f422430181e3050fefe","tid":1023542,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:48:55.000Z","msg":"駁我就原形畢露<br />\n唯有當睇唔到"},{"pid":"916a2584893701fc0c4f7ac46e3616a345d1ac9e","tid":1023542,"uid":138409,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7d139f5e29d7ac6471d2642230025eef21ecf49c","tid":1023542,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:48:53.000Z","msg":"估都估到<br />\n真既話中共會比人拍片咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:54:14.000Z","msg":"咁又好難講嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前都有人偷拍咗新疆集中營內部<br />\n<br />\n不過呢件事令我想起<br />\n近排睇咗睇猶太人大屠殺歷史嘅書<br />\n二戰期間，外國媒體乃至於士兵都相當懷疑集中營暴行嘅消息<br />\n其中原因正正係一次大戰時候呢類「敵方戰爭惡行」流料太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到「狼來了」"},{"pid":"8628e1dcba1e6a501d8e31cd0b63baab343148ef","tid":1023542,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T02:00:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"80b50eb702abd07c242702670d0b1bde9d78cdc3","tid":1023542,"uid":9958,"like":1,"disl